Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.13,0:00:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, isn't dropping out of school kinda reckless?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we wait until graduation at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who hesitate long enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...Don't make it anywhere in life!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the venue manager told us so!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.06,0:00:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But... how are we even\Nsupposed to tell our parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- How about taking a sabbatical?\N- Oh! That could work!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That way we can still\Ngo back to school after.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me.\NWe're gonna make it for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The agency told us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That we'll revolutionize the\N{\i1}girls band{\i0} genre,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That we'll definitely hit it big in Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And that they'll get us a {\i1}major debut!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we'll\Nhit it off {\i1}that{\i0} well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.38,0:00:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And when did they tell\Nus to drop out of school?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:00:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.39,0:01:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.85,0:01:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Always so confident...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If we leave an escape route,\Nwe'll definitely be tempted to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Having somewhere to run away to\Nwill just distract us from moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.78,0:01:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.78,0:01:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because it's a difficult path\Nthat it has to be all or nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.66,0:01:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}AIM FOR THE BUDOKAN!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make it to the Budokan together!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So... should we stop for a toilet break?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.76,0:01:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all ears, Momoka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.39,0:01:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.52,0:01:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop provoking her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:01:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Noted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Start by apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}8: IF YOU WERE TO CRY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i0}Me{\i1}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru-chan? Why are you siding with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not siding with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, shouldn't bring this up\Nduring a concert of all places.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The stage is for our customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sacred place!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a place for you to vent\Nabout your personal matters!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's exactly why I wanted to say it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So that you'd listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down you two, we're in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've expected you of all\Npeople would've stopped her, Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? I've already given up on stopping her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just embarassing, I'm heading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you won't want to miss this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who should be apologizing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You just quit without consulting\N any of us? You're gonna end it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna hear this from the one\Nwho decided we'll go pro without asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut from the same cloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, wasn't this your plan to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Real sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pushing forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep getting fired up like a\Ndumbass if you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're gonna regret this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even realize how popular\NDiamond Dust has gotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's even more reason to\Nnot give up without even trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's even more reason to want to prove...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...That we weren't wrong!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:04:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being delusional.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0}'re the one who is trying\Nto look away from reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you even know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then tell me!! Why did you\Ncontinue with this band to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really thought you weren't up to it anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why didn't you go back home on that day?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why start a band again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, all things aside, don't drop out of school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever floats your boat then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't run awa--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all acting for a TV show!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are heating up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Punch me if you want. I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably better that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,At least that will give me a\N reason to hate you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll be no different from {\i1}them{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So it ends once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally done...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, finally free of that horrid atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you get that guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it when we were leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That an issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You.. got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine-san gifted her a spare guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she couldn't help it\Nwith how "real and genuine" her voice felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She wanted to encourage her\Nbecause she's just like you, she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:07:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let them know you'll be returning the van then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry, I'll be stopping here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can drive you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bit of a pain with all the traffic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Trains are still running, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't forget the meds\Nfor your motion sickness, Tomo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me {\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- See you later, then.\N- Drive safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are trains still running at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just thought I'd lend you an ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling considerate today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta say, I've always liked\Nthe chill vibe of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Should move to a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna come once a room frees up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? I'd have to think twice before\Ndeciding to be your roommate...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Rupa and the others know\Nthat Nina was gonna say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess we should've seen it coming,\Nwith how gung-ho she's been lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you stop her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a free world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You of all people should know\Nhow reckless she's being.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even as an indie band, \Nwe haven't released anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got accepted into\Nthe festival, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rupa-san has also received an offer from a label.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you're a former Diamond Dust member.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo-chan and Rupa-san too,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They've already got a rep online as a mystery duo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And just recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain vocalist tweeted\Nabout really liking Nina's voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It got quite a bit of traction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already got this many followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}27,851 FOLLOWERS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And in a survey for who the customers\Nare coming for in the next show...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...We ranked number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite what you said, Nina isn't delusional.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:09:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's not like we can compete\Nwith DD or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're at least making a big step in the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...What did the other two say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They were always planning to go pro, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tag along~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone grows up eventually
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were all in on it, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just... that it's like Nina puts it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're serious about this,\Nit's gotta be all or nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's because it's a difficult path\Nthat it has to be all or nothing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Gonna need one of these...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And, uuuh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,One of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...Should be enough for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A minor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,F.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sol.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:10:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, anyone could do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}FREEDOM, FREEDOM,\NFrom todAy i've become fREEEE!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}TodAy and tomOrrOw\NI'll doO the things i lIKEEE!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Chaka-chang!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear father,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.07,0:10:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you for raising me until now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be working hard on my own now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You don't need to send me any more money.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}BUMPKINBANK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll send you back the bank card too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Regards, Nina.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}To: Iseri Muneo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome one, welcome all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you, a sushi place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch... is that not good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just say "hello" like a normal person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times have you been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the type to pay attention to details...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially as a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yum.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat that and you're fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.61,0:11:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, why did you have to\Ncome work here of all places?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my first time working, so I thought it'd\Nbe better to be with someone I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, goddamit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What country did she crawl from?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's sure got a mouth for a {\i1}foreigner{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for the delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch, you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your patronage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Rupa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a daily occurrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you, I need rock to vent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go check the soup stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how are things with Momoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's really changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we tried to talk,\Nwe'd probably end up fighting again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll repeat myself, but if this fallout\Ncontinues, we're leaving too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, welcooooo... {\i1}ome?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,One medium.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,One medium!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like a beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to order?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have time after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Girls Band Cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}See, she didn't mean any harm or wanted to bully you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You two just got into an argument, and her hand slipped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You understand ...right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a relief.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, I want the both of you to write an apology,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So let's make up with a good handshake!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Iseri-san...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're close, we'll be there in a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that seeing you driving now...\NI don't think I hate it that much anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They could at least send a message\Nto let us know how it's going...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Have faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The opposite of love is indifference after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,For two people to still try to talk things out\Neven after all that arguing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.19,0:13:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's proof of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Or proof of idiocy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just open the door and you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What can I even rely on, is there anything like that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}People always tell me to just do it by the book.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But its words are so complex I dunno where to look{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My today hasn't changed in all these years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Dust...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what {\i1}all or nothing{\i0} means.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not having the luxury to sing what you really want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to make a living,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to ask yourself: What sells?\NWhat does everyone like? What's trendy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Pushing through a never-ending cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...But that isn't true for everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The artists who are able to\Ncreate what they really want...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...Are but a handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I USED TO BE YOUR FAN, BUT NOT ANYMORE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the other original members of DD...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Without Momoka it's dogshit now\NIt's so over for them lmao\NFucking hate the vocalist\NWhatever\NAt least she's hot\NIs it me or does DD kinda suck ass now?\NThe DD I loved is dead\NQutting as a fan from today\NYou've let me down for the last time\NThey need a reality check
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.91,0:14:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...Didn't wanna go down this path.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is what they chose. To make a living. To keep living.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not a guarantee\Nthat your music wouldn't sell, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Before it even got the chance, you gave up on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And quit the band before even trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But the reality is that they\Nsucceeded by doing the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what DD was meant to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, all of us kept saying:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Screw all those idol wannabes playing it safe!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"We're gonna make it with {\i1}our{\i0} music!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But it fell on deaf ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}FOR: MOMOKA OF DIAMOND DUST
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The reality is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you've got the talent,\Nif you can't sell, you can't sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What we used to scoff at became\Nthe only songs that would blow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the world of entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The pressure of reality began to weigh on us,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So we had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If we rejected it, we wouldn't have been able to push forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They chose to continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's not a right I can deny them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't want {\i1}you{\i0} to have\Nto make the same choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked why I didn't go back home\Nand formed a new band, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw you singing back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...I saw my younger self in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't care about what sold or being validated,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You just sang what you loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Nina I loved the most,\Nbecause it reminded me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...Of who I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I wanted you to keep singing as yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not chained by anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to hear you sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you very much!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are Diamond Dust!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make some noise for the next band too, okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about {\i1}my{\i0} feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about {\i1}MY{\i0} feelings?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not part of your backstory!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't you dare chain me to your memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So let's make up with a good handshake!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs28}Is it even possible to fill this void?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Iseri-san...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs48}Maybe someday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it were up to you, would you keep going?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Iseri-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nina, wait!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This void feeling,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This eternal feeling,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of answers that lead to superficial clichés...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if {\i1}your{\i0} fingers tremble...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...your songs still gave me the strength to live!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What you really should be protecting
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the you from your memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But your desire to reach others with your music!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanting to convey your feelings, your joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Your anger, your sorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the real reason why you stared a band, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you started singing at school, right?!\NWhy you came to Tokyo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you wanted to connect, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:18:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you scared of?\NWhat are you chickening out for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm living proof!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That there's someone who has been saved by you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand you,\Nbut you gave me the courage to fly!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who was so overjoyed\Nto just sing alongside you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who's been willing\Nto bet everything on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who always\Nbelieved in you... and your music!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't run away because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey!\N- ...Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving. Get home by train.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san, wait! Momoka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When there's no need for you to run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When you've done nothing wrong!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to\Nspeak to us, just listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard you started a new band!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us what you got!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're shooting for the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll prove to you we weren't wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll keep making a living until we do, so...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't intend to lose either!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:20:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make you admit that this...\Nis what we're meant to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll prove to you that we weren't wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So whimsical...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What gives you the right to act so mighty
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,After that dogshit of a\Nperformance you put on?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna be idols?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've got no regrets, then play the part of the cute girl better, goddamit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pros, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.30,0:20:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be squaring off at the next festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And after your snooze of a performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll steal every last one of your customers!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that even mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A declaration of war!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll never forget, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.71,0:20:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:20:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.46,0:21:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck.
